This directory contains code for the GPU, developed in collaboration
with Genady Yoffe and Xiangcheng Yu, 
written mainly for the NVIDIA Tesla C2050 and K20C.

The directories are organized in chronological order:

PED : Polynomial Evaluation and Differentiation,
      the paper was presented at PDSEC 2012 in Shanghai.

MGS : version of modified Gram-Schmidt method,
      the paper was presented at PDSEC 2013 in Boston.

MGS2 : second version of MGS2 works for larger dimensions.

